###  https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#UndeterminedJourney
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#UndeterminedJourney> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                rdfs:subClassOf <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#PlannedJourneyOrPath> ;
                                                rdfs:comment "Undetermined journey might be the correct expression in EN-speaking areas (unregulated train seems to exist but seems to be related to dispatcher roles, hence avoided here). At SNCF, was called \" marche indeterminee (abbr. MI)\"." ;
                                                rdfs:label "Undetermined journey"@en .


###  https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#VersionedDescription
<https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#VersionedDescription> rdf:type owl:Class ;
