                                                                 prov:Entity ,
                                                                 <https://cdm.ovh/rsm/operations/rope/rope#OperationalEntity> ;
                                                 rdfs:comment "A description (e.g. of a schedule, or other operational specs such as orders issued to drivers) that can be revised, and is effective (= applicable) from a certain datetime. The versions are chained as a simple list (nop forks, no loops)."@en ;
                                                 rdfs:label "Versioned description" .


